# Demo: sudo
  - Create user:              sudo useradd bob
  - Change user:              su bob; whoami
  - Who has sudo permissions: sudo less /etc/sudoers
  - Show groups:              groups
  - Shadow:                   cat /etc/shadow
  - Sudo shadow:              sudo cat /etc/shadow
  - Badsudo shadow:           ./sudo cat /etc/shadow

